1LT Overton;

Greetings.

I've been making adjustments to the above subject document, based upon the
recommendations from the Orders Consistency Review.

Here are the changes that I made, according to the numbering on the AI
results:

1, The main execution day is 14 MAY 26 the exercise, and actions supporting
the exercise will occur during the time period of 12 - 15 MAY 26.. This is
not a RGT S1 task, it is a task to DIV G1. We won't be providing anyone to
the DIV Mob Cell.
2. I have revised the time-line in the Phasing in Paragraph 3(b)(2).
3. This is not a RGT S1 task, it is a task to DIV G1. We won't be providing
anyone to the DIV Mob Cell.
4. I added a line and tasks for the 61 Med attachment and S3 / S4
coordination.
5. I dropped the VTS sites from the AO description.
6. I cited the TNNG LOI and requested a copy from the TNNG POC, MAJ
Callison.

